  "text": "The paper [CITATION_1] proposes a Petri-net-based design and verification tool for web service composition. The tool can visualize, create, and verify business processes. The authors are now improving the graphical user interface which can be used to aid the business process modeling and to edit Petri Net and BPEL in a lump.",
